Award winning Nigerian producer and Mavin records boss, Don Jazzy is of the opinion that there are too many artistes in Nigeria’s music industry. In a series of tweets, Don Jazzy opined that what the industry needs right now is more song writers to increase the quality of lyrical contents, saying not everyone will blow as an artiste. While addressing the proliferation of music artistes in Nigeria, Don Jazzy said, there are more vacant positions to be filled up in the industry other than being on stage. However, the award winning producer announced his upcoming projects that will see songwriters become more recognized in Nigeria as well as become richer than music artistes. See Tweets Below;      The post The Industry Needs More Song Writers, We Have Too Many Artistes  – Don Jazzy appeared first on 360Nobs.com.   Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from 360Nobs.com. Click here to read the full text on the original website.